quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  14,28,"Ese ntiwabonye babandi baguranye inema za Allah, (aho gushimira) bagahakana; maze bagatuma abantu babo batura mu nzu y’uburimbukiro"
  14,29,(Iyo nzu ni umuriro wa) Jahanamu bazinjiramo kandi ni bwo buturo bubi
  14,30,"Kandi (ababangikanyamana) bashyizeho ibigirwamana babibangikanya na Allah kugira ngo bayobye (abantu) inzira ye. Vuga uti \"Nimwinezeze (by’igihe gito)! Ariko mu by’ukuri, iherezo ryanyu ni mu muriro"
  14,31,"(Yewe Muhamadi) bwira abagaragu banjye bemeye, ko bagomba guhozaho amasengesho bakanatanga mu byo twabahaye; haba mu ibanga cyangwa ku mugaragaro, mbere y’uko haza umunsi utazabamo ubucuruzi n’ubucuti (bigamije gucungura)"
  14,32,"Allah ni we waremye ibirere n’isi anamanura amazi (imvura) mu kirere, nuko ayameresha imbuto kugira ngo zibabere amafunguro; yanaborohereje amato kugira ngo agendere mu nyanja ku itegeko rye, ndetse yanaborohereje imigezi (kugira ngo ibagirire akamaro)"
  14,33,"Yanaborohereje izuba n’ukwezi bihora bizenguruka mu buryo butunganye, ndetse anaborohereza ijoro n’amanywa (kugira ngo byose bibagirire akamaro)"
  14,34,"Yanabahaye ibyo mwamusabye byose, kandi muramutse mushatse kubarura inema za Allahntimwazihetura. Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ni inkozi y’ibibi ya cyane, umuhakanyi ukabije (w’indashima)"